# --- Shopify headless (Storefront API) ---
# Copy this file to ".env.local" (which is git-ignored) and fill in your values.
# In production, set the same variables in your Vercel project settings.
#
# 1. In Shopify admin: Settings → Apps and sales channels → Develop apps
#    → Create an app → Configure Storefront API scopes
#    (enable: read_products, read_product_listings; for cart/checkout later:
#     unauthenticated_read_product_listings, unauthenticated_write_checkouts).
# 2. Install the app, then copy the "Storefront API access token".
#
# Your store's *.myshopify.com domain (NOT the custom domain):
SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN=your-store.myshopify.com

# The Storefront API access token from your custom app:
SHOPIFY_STOREFRONT_TOKEN=your_storefront_api_token_here
